        <abstract> 
<p>Has observed rare instances of <hi rend="italic">Ophrys apifera</hi> with "cut labellum". Suggests it was done by large dragonfly mistaking the flower for a fly visiting a flower. Stimulated to study <hi rend="italic">Ophrys</hi> by <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>.</p> 
